{"tid":355871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"試找出「肥絲大隻」的錯別字","createTime":"2017-08-11T15:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T15:46:43.000Z","uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6772f9fe16f39ba372470787b0e22e0abbd274e6","tid":355871,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/233823_f0ffac665043b89f27dd9d00739445ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F233823_f0ffac665043b89f27dd9d00739445ac.jpg&h=0886929d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n同<del>男朋友</del><span style=\"color: red;\">條仔</span>一齊差<del>唔</del><span style=\"color: red;\">吾</span>多五年，我為左佢改變<del>咗</del><span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>好多，以前我都仲會同佢講我嘅唔開心，但佢話我好戇鳩，慢慢我只會同佢分享我嘅開心，而唔開心嘅我都收埋。<br />\n<br />\n有一次我覺得好煩好驚，我同佢講，佢話我好煩，我嘅煩惱搞到佢都煩埋，叫我唔好再講，之後我就唔敢再講，連朋友都唔講。<br />\n<br />\n而且一齊左咁多年，每次鬧交（如果係街，佢都要我街埋一邊比佢鬧，佢鬧完就好似冇野咁拖住手繼續行，我只可以去迎合）我覺得係條街企係到比佢鬧好似老豆鬧女，我覺得好瘀。好似做戲咁，係條街比佢羞辱。<br />\n<br />\n而且男朋友好鍾意每次鬧完交，都同佢媽講返今日鬧交嘈左啲咩...仲要係我面前講...我覺得無地自容..."},{"pid":"5dfd277349dfdc0b531cac1ba4a5c2ee8eab65a7","tid":355871,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"382301dd0fe395192348f5ac8da9b8a67079ce5f","tid":355871,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再幫條垃圾上位啦"},{"pid":"921cc23f1abdb96d364c577db4869e669cfa2ddb","tid":355871,"uid":60156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"過主啦"},{"pid":"f65de4d91cd7c2320d8870aedc19fbfc768cbb3b","tid":355871,"uid":93533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以好似格嚟po 高質少少啊？<br />\n想呃正皮都比少少心機諗吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似你呢種低質肥絲po已經變咗做日經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}